_source.body: I'm following Eric Zemmour's French presidential bid with interest. Obviously I'm greatly encouraged that he is putting the #GreatReplacement and the very tangible threat to European civilisation at the centre of his campaign - But his domestic policy appears sound enough too, including his pledge to rural communities, local producers and businesses. However, the 'vision thing' - good old IDEALISM is almost totally absent from domestic politics today, so Zemmour's Mont-Saint-Michel speech tomorrow, where he promises to speak on "our right to greatness and our duty to power!" sounds promising. We need more romanticism and utopianism in our political discourse - because they INSPIRE. Inspiration nurtures action! #zemmour  #zemmour2022 #zemmourpresident
